<tr><td align=right>Issue:</td><td><b>Issue 6, October 2000</b></td></tr>
<tr><td align=right>Section:</td><td><b>News & Gossip</b></td></tr>
<tr><td align=right>Author:</td><td><b><span class="missing">Tattler</span></b></td></tr>
